* Fix hunk colorization.

== 0.1.5 2010-03-10

* Add --[no-]color and colorize diff output by default.

* Read user's preferred default options from DI_OPTIONS.

== 0.1.4 2010-03-10

* Add --[no-]pager and turn it on by default.

* Do not choke on file names starting with a hyphen.

== 0.1.3 2010-03-10

* Fix handling of the following options and make custom format options
  work:
    -D/--ifdef=NAME
    --GTYPE-group-format=GFMT
    --line-format=LFMT
    --LTYPE-line-format=LFMT

* Fix a problem where escape sequence ESC $ B .. : is regarded as CVS
  keyword, which often appears in a text encoded in ISO-2022-JP.

== 0.1.1 2008-10-06

* Initial release
